race.comment: GREENIDGE (3) looks ready to bounce back after fading late as favourite over 1400m at Penola. Drops to a preferred trip and is unbeaten at this venue. Plenty to like. GUSTY WAY (8) charged home for second when resuming over 1075m and will relish the extra ground second-up. Tough to hold out. ROCKTAGON (9) has been narrowly beaten in his last two and gets Pannell to offset the wide draw. Due for a breakthrough and should be right there again. CAPTAIN JOOLIAN (2) improved sharply second-up and steps out over further with added fitness. Crowther reunites and he's a genuine winning chance.
